OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779293476
OL,3,CPortsmouth landmark restored ahead of
OL,4,Ccity's centenary celebrations
OL,6,FThe iconic sails at the entrance of
OL,7,FPortsmouth have been restored in time
OL,8,Ffor the city's centenary celebrations.
OL,10,FThe city council said the fabric on
OL,11,Fthe tri-sail structure on the M275 had
OL,12,Freached the end of its 25-year design
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,FThe sails have now all been replaced
OL,16,Fand structural checks and lighting
OL,17,Fupgrades have been carried out to
OL,18,Fensure it meets modern safety
OL,19,Fstandards and the wider structure
OL,20,Ffulfils its intended 50-year lifespan.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
