PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779293476
OL,3,CPortsmouth landmark restored ahead of
OL,4,Ccity's centenary celebrations
OL,6,FIn order for the work to be carried
OL,7,Fout on the Sails of the South
OL,8,Flandmark, the traffic was slowed for
OL,9,Fshort periods instead of implementing
OL,10,Ffull motorway lane closures.
OL,12,FThe city council says this meant
OL,13,Ftraffic could continue moving and
OL,14,Fbuses could remain on time, whilst
OL,15,Fcrews worked on the restoration.
OL,17,FCllr Steve Pitt, Leader of Portsmouth
OL,18,FCity Council, said: "The Sails of the
OL,19,FSouth are an iconic symbol of
OL,20,FPortsmouth, welcoming people into our
OL,21,Fcity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
