CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779293476
OL,3,CPortsmouth landmark restored ahead of
OL,4,Ccity's centenary celebrations
OL,6,F"I'm delighted that this refurbishment
OL,7,Fis now complete, restoring the
OL,8,Fstructure so it looks its best for the
OL,9,Fcity's Portsmouth100 celebrations, and
OL,10,Fremains safe and resilient for many
OL,11,Fyears to come."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
